{"tid":2336203,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"伊院86歲男病人離世　屬歌舞群組　本港累計132人染疫亡","createTime":"2020-12-22T12:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T13:11:05.000Z","uid":54337,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1da6f492d61e0ddcc1cc16238159c8423c6dfa9c","tid":2336203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:07:08.000Z","msg":"伊院86歲男病人離世 屬歌舞群組 本港累計132人染疫亡<br />\n<br />\n伊利沙伯醫院發言人今(22日)公布，一名有長期病患的86歲男病人，於11月27日因咳嗽入住伊院接受治療，其後確診新冠肺炎，病人情況持續惡化，延至今日凌晨1時14分離世。院方對病人離世感到難過，會為家屬提供適切協助。病人生前居於鑽石山宏景花園2座，屬歌舞群組相關個案。<br />\n連同上述病人，至今共有132名確診者離世。"},{"pid":"678c0422b5ac7b7e0228fc20dd996c40a35ccceb","tid":2336203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:07:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201222/mobile/bkn-20201222151434110-1222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201222%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201222151434110-1222_00822_001.html&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=8f66dff7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201222/mobile/bkn-20201222151434110-1222_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c83e26a33e962288a6e488668f9ef558118f3e0e","tid":2336203,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"86碎就抵死啦"},{"pid":"77897cfca90faeaa3be8fe1606cde36619dcc742","tid":2336203,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:08:08.000Z","msg":"本身都o個頭近,當係笑喪啦"},{"pid":"c00d98dd5757c7fa9ba366ca824483c46666a477","tid":2336203,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T12:08:14.000Z","msg":"跳舞跳到過埋奈何橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822bf503325d2db6817d98098ff813c6990a938b","tid":2336203,"uid":98385,"lik